48.plot: Epic wing suit stunts, not-so epic male gymnastics, and a motorcyclist gets swept up in a flood. Oh, and a snow skier dressed as Santa Clause crashes into a picnic table.

49.title: One Sweet Fail
49.plot: Extreme motorcycle stunts, not-so extreme skateboarding, and two para gliders collide midair. Oh, and a guy balances on a yoga ball while playing a bagpipe.

50.title: Random Acts of Failure
50.plot: Incredible hang gliding, not-so incredible long boarding, and a horse and buggy collides with a truck on a highway. Oh, and a group of guys hit the gym in full armor.

51.title: Fails for Sale
51.plot: Awesome wing suits, not-so awesome trikes, and a llama attacks a snow skier. Oh, and a man on stilts tries to run on a treadmill - unsuccessfully.

52.title: The Final Fail
52.plot: Epic paragliding, not-so epic rollerblading, and a guy catches a football while doing a back flip on a wake board. Oh, and a man rides a shopping cart down a set of stairs.

imdb.title: What Went Down
plot: Every thirty minute episode of _What Went Down_ (qv) is a home run derby of the world's most incredible collection of sports screw-ups, epic fails, and embarrassing outcomes. Witness it all yourself and celebrate the human spirit.
